column6:
Wayne Lynch is one of the primary pioneers of the 70s shortboard revolution. This "fun" range is a development from his performance range. Slighty wider with a touch more volume with slighty softer curves. But boy do they have power!! Tuflite contruction, Round Pin Tail


Information about shipping costs:

For the shipment of surfboards within the European Union we have to add 40 EUR shipping costs, outside the European Union 80 EUR have to be added.
The shipment will be done by DHL including transport incurance.
After ordering your surfboard, you will be contacted by our customer service concerning the shipping costs.
